FW Caminus Zainet Access Cc Original Message From Cantu Lupita On Behalf Of ETS Information Risk Management Sent Monday September PM To McCary Sandy Cc ETS Information Risk Management Subject RE Caminus Zainet Access Users listed below have been added to the requested group Changes will take effect on the next login Thanks Lupita Cantu ETS Information Risk Management Original Message From McCary Sandy Sent Monday September AM To ETS Information Risk Management Subject FW Caminus Zainet Access Please add the following users to application group AppCaminus Zainet Mark McConnell and Paul YBarbo Thanks Sandy Original Message From Strohmeyer Vincent Sent Monday September AM To McCary Sandy Cc Watson Kimberly McConnell Mark YBarbo Paul Subject Caminus Zainet Access Sandy please add Mark McConnell and Paul YBarbo to the Caminus Zainet users list per Kim Watsons request Thanks Vince Strohmeyer Paul and Mark You should be able to get into the Caminus system as outlined below after you have been added to the user group To initiate the installation of the Caminus ZaiNet application the users should perform the following Click Start button Click Programs menu Click Business Applications menu Double click the Caminus ZaiNet option After you reboot your system you will be able to log in to Caminus Zainet Your User ID is your first and last initials followed by the numbers eg Fred Flintstone would be FF and your initial password is password You will be prompted to change your password on initial log in Thanks Vince Strohmeyer

ETS Marketing Dashboard Access Cc You have been granted access to the ETS Marketing Dashboard URL Userid mmcconne Password mmcconne You may change your password at any time after the initial login by clicking on the Profile link in the upperright hand corner of the Dashboard and then clicking on the Change Password link You will be receiving another email shortly once your security privileges have been established for the Pipeline Profile If you have any questions please feel free to give me a call Thanks Sandy x
